Disclaimer: The food here is SPECTACULAR! I have been to this place a few times and had a mostly positive experience throughout. This review is STRICTLY with respect to the lack of urgency of a situation I encountered during my last visit. Specifically, I found a piece of glass in my food last week and notified them immediately that night. However, I decided to go back to give them another shot tonight and was frustrated for two reasons: 1) a clear lack of urgency for the issue that I experienced with the glass, and 2) a lack of consistency in presentation and quality. Not to be trivial, but I received fries about less than a handful and was shocked, since they forgot to include an order of fries during my last visit. This entire experience was very serious for me as I almost swallowed the glass and did not appreciate it being shrugged off tonight. Luckily, that was not my 3-year-old nephew's order. I hope they remedy these issues because the food here is really great and is a great addition to the neighborhood.
